Privacy Notice (Updated 4/22/22)

Your Privacy is our Priority

1. Cookies
When using services offered by hodss.xyz and TSSCAC we may use some essential cookies ot allow site function. These may be things like signup and login cookies. Otherwise, there are no other cookies.

2. Analytics
We use JuSoft Insights to gather analytical information. Your data is secure, and your information is deleted after 7 days.

3. Storage of data
Locations of storage servers are: The United Kingdom, The United States of America. Your data is secure and non essential data (e.g. payment information) is deleted after 7 days. We may keep your email and password to ensure the correct usage of our sites and login systems.

4. Our Right to change this policy and notice
We have the right to change this policy with a 3 day notice and if you are a registered user or on a mailing list (which you can be part of by emailing hod@hodss.xyz and asking to be apart of the newsletter/mailing list.) you will be notified via email.

5. Data handling
Contact hod@hodss.xyz to have your data removed immediately.
